body:
Captain Marvel Design Changes

So we all know about how captain marvel was glammed up a bit from her movie to endgame

And we were all a bit salty but whatever.

I just noticed that they changed her suit too for the final battle. (Left) original (right) Endgame.

The suit is tighter, more form fitting. Her boobs are incredibly accentuated where they weren’t before and the armor give the impression of abs. The gold at her hips make them seem bigger and more pronounced and it looks like somehow her thighs are smaller.

Captain Marvel’s costume was changed to be more sexually appealing and I am not okay with that.
